title: Symba has NEXT!
description:
Jalen & Jacoby are joined by ascending, impending SUPERSTAR: Symba. His new album, "Results Take Time" hosted by DJ Drama drops Friday, and you need to check it out. He dishes on his grind, getting co-signed by Dr. Dre, LeBron, KD and other stars, what we should expect from the album, and why his Warriors are going to repeat as champs. Plus! The guys break down tonight's massive Chiefs-Chargers game, Donovan Mitchell torturing (some) Knicks fans, and LeBron's reaction to the Sarver punishment. Tap in!
